{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tag-js","path":"/blog/tag/pact","result":{"data":{"wpgraphql":{"tag":{"id":"cG9zdF90YWc6MjQyNw==","name":"PACT","slug":"pact","posts":{"nodes":[{"id":"cG9zdDo0OTMz","title":"Timeline: Transforming the Business Industry in 18 Months","uri":"plastic-straws-businesses-timeline-singapore/","slug":"plastic-straws-businesses-timeline-singapore","date":"2019-06-04T19:26:49","content":"<p>A breakdown of how we helped transform the business landscape in Singapore to reduce plastic use. Starting 1 July 2019, more than 270 F&amp;B outlets from 32 brands will be phasing out straws as part of PACT (Plastic ACTion), a WWF initiative for businesses to reduce plastic use. This is a major industry-wide effort supported [&hellip;]</p>\n","author":{"name":"Sharon Salim","slug":"ssalim","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e36b8ae309f36dfc7c9fe446f89fd97d?s=100&d=mm&r=g"}},"tags":{"nodes":[{"name":"accorhotels group","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/accorhotels-group/","slug":"accorhotels-group"},{"name":"business roundtables","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/business-roundtables/","slug":"business-roundtables"},{"name":"kraftwich","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/kraftwich/","slug":"kraftwich"},{"name":"PACT","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/pact/","slug":"pact"},{"name":"pastamania","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/pastamania/","slug":"pastamania"},{"name":"plastic action","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/plastic-action/","slug":"plastic-action"},{"name":"plastic reduction","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/plastic-reduction/","slug":"plastic-reduction"},{"name":"plastic straws","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/plastic-straws/","slug":"plastic-straws"},{"name":"pontiac land group","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/pontiac-land-group/","slug":"pontiac-land-group"},{"name":"ramada and days hotels","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/ramada-and-days-hotels/","slug":"ramada-and-days-hotels"}]},"categories":{"nodes":[{"name":"Plastics in Nature","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/category/plastics-in-nature/","slug":"plastics-in-nature"}]},"campaigns":{"nodes":[]},"featuredImage":{"sourceUrl":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/BEFORE-17.png","altText":"","srcSet":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/BEFORE-17-300x158.png 300w, https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/BEFORE-17.png 600w"}},{"id":"cG9zdDo0MDI5","title":"Salad Stop!’s Katherine Braha on Building a Sustainable Business","uri":"salad-stop-katherine-braha-sustainable-no-plastic/","slug":"salad-stop-katherine-braha-sustainable-no-plastic","date":"2019-01-30T18:14:56","content":"<p>Co-founder and director of Salad Stop! Katherine Braha is not only passionate about everything marketing-related, but the mother-of-one is also pushing the brand to go plastic-free. SaladStop! has joined PACT, a voluntary business-led Plastic ACTion commitment on plastic. Since the start of 2019, the sustainable food business has implemented a plastic and paper bag charge [&hellip;]</p>\n","author":{"name":"Sharon Salim","slug":"ssalim","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e36b8ae309f36dfc7c9fe446f89fd97d?s=100&d=mm&r=g"}},"tags":{"nodes":[{"name":"katherine braha","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/katherine-braha/","slug":"katherine-braha"},{"name":"no plastics in nature","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/no-plastics-in-nature/","slug":"no-plastics-in-nature"},{"name":"PACT","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/pact/","slug":"pact"},{"name":"plastics free","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/plastics-free/","slug":"plastics-free"},{"name":"saladstop!","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheonsite.io/tag/saladstop/","slug":"saladstop"},{"name":"single-use plastics","link":"https://dev-wwfsg.pantheons